[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/preemptive_bids"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

You have four quick winners. If partner had opened 3\H you would have bid 4\H in the blink of an eye. His Weak Jump Overcall describes the exact same hand. So blink and bid 4\H.}

